sequenceDiagram
  participant CI as CI Server
  participant Repo as Repository
  participant Kind as Kind Cluster
  participant K8s as Kubernetes
  participant Test as Integration Tests
  CI->>Repo: Checkout code
  CI->>Kind: Create Kind cluster
  CI->>K8s: Deploy manifests
  K8s->>K8s: Pods start
  K8s-->>CI: Pods ready signal
  CI->>Test: Execute integration tests
  Test-->>CI: Test results
  CI->>Kind: Delete Kind cluster
